All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
Application
Main class of the Spring Boot application.
Cart
Represents a shopping cart for the customer
CartItem
Represents a line item in the shopping cart
CartItemRepository
This interface provides the necessary methods to interact with the database for the CartItem entity.
CartItemService
This class provides business logic for CartItem entities.
CartRepository
This interface provides methods for interacting with the database table "cart".
CartService
This class provides services for managing a customer's shopping cart.
Customer
Represents a Customer
CustomerController
This class is the customer controller that handles all the requests related to the customer.
CustomerRepository
This interface is used to define the methods that will be used to interact with the Customer table in the database.
CustomerService
This service provides operations for managing customers in the system.
Product
Represents products in the online shop
ProductController
 
ProductRepository
This interface provides methods for interacting with the database table "product".
ProductService
This class provides business logic for managing products in the system.
